        "cooked": "<ol>\n<li>Correct. Taking a snapshot does not affect the mutation log stored somewhere.</li>\n<li>Correct.</li>\n<li>Correct. But see p 2.</li>\n<li>What do you mean as \u201cAdditional versions of data\u201d? If you clear a key from the main primary database, the same key will be cleared from the DR database after a short timelag.</li>\n<li>Correct.</li>\n</ol>",
